{"tid":1652954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整旗團隊!!!  可否整埋訴求既旗","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T02:45:22.000Z","uid":105976,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd8caf7d8a9c2c2555b0be0b024afc0b63b009e","tid":1652954,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:55.000Z","msg":"外媒搵唔到新野報<br />\n和理非唱歌 叫口號 係有聲 但外國人又聽唔明<br />\n我地自己又欠一個焦點<br />\n<br />\n大家唱榮光果陣有冇發現好似少咁d野俾你望住 唔知望邊度好<br />\n係 係旗, 但圖案旗爭議太大<br />\n建議大家印d 5/6大訴求旗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;普選&quot; &quot;獨立調查&quot; 英文 中文 既旗<br />\n咁樣明標會清楚好多 俾外媒睇亦俾自已睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武就唔建議拎啦 影響走佬<br />\n<br />\n如果冇其他團隊整我地就開工<br />\n聯絡:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/MacFfpZG75cLPQcv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FMacFfpZG75cLPQcv8&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=46bc3007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/MacFfpZG75cLPQcv8</a>"},{"pid":"82293330b478c0742c7f02dff0b4741075f645d4","tid":1652954,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d78480fb1ad359762975b67340f16b8681d7f0b","tid":1652954,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5013024f5660960a8d029facb339278b28d97635","tid":1652954,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8247c3c168d5cbafb67f2ab70d9edc968be2d3e","tid":1652954,"uid":21575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n郭榮鏗喺881引述Ted話眾議院通過法案問題不大，但參議院會有阻力，希望大家暫時停止暴力，唔好被人利用"},{"pid":"4609a536f24e93e8b2af04c869c962a4bfb4943e","tid":1652954,"uid":835